| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2823 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 832d1508-99b1-5d7e-83f3-19cee994cbf9"
